<module status="bronze">
    <h>stad</h>
    <p><g>stad</g>
        <en>stop, halt, pause, rest, stall, cease, desist, come/bring to a stop/halt</en> is a
        (regular) <a href="?xx=verbs/verbs">verb</a>, marking <a href="?q=verbal_aspect"
            >cessative</a> verbal aspect, cf. <a href="?gd=sguir"><g>sguir</g></a>
        <vb/>
        <en>stop, cease</en>, <a href="?gd=crìoch"><g>crìoch</g></a>
        <fem/>
        <en>end, boundary</en>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>stad</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>stadaidh</m> – future independent ie. <en>will stop</en></li>
                <li><m>stad</m> – past independent ie. <en>stopped</en></li>
                <li><m>stad</m> (<g>stadadh</g>) – verbal noun ie. <en>stopping</en></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <section>
            <h>tense</h>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>past <ul id="past">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>stad</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>stad</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do stad</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>stadadh</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>stadadh</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do stadadh</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>future <ul id="future">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>stadaidh</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>stadas</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>stad</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>stadar</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>stadar</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>stadar</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>conditional <ul id="conditional">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>first person singular <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>stadainn</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>stadainn</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>stadainn</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>first person plural <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>stadamaid</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>stadamaid</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>stadamaid</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>second/third persons <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>stadadh</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>stadadh</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>stadadh</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>stadte</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>stadte</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>stadte</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
